title: USI HD1200 Heavy Duty Thermal Pouch Laminator, Laminates Pouches up to 12 Inches Wide and 15 Mil Thick; 5-Year Warranty, Made in The USA
features: High quality, heavy duty machine that laminates documents up to 12 inches wide and up to 15 mil thick.
Compatible with many pouch sizes: business card, credit card, photo, letter, and legal.
Laminates uses a laminating carrier (included) to keep rollers clean. 5-year warranty.
MADE IN THE USA by USI...the lamination leader since 1975!
description: The HD 1200 heavy duty thermal pouch laminator is ideal for office, industrial and health care environments. The HD 1200 is built to withstand constant use. This quality machine is the quietest on the market and has an adjustable temperature control for laminating pouch films up to 15 mil thick each side. Perfect for protecting documents, making custom displays, creating IDs and much more. MADE IN THE USA!
